window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Wandmaker, Amethyst, is certain that her lot in life is to make wands for her fellow witches. Until a Detective shows up at her shop asking for help only she can give.&nbsp;</p> <p>One taste of an investigation, and Amethyst is thrown into the world of mystery and crime. Can she use her skills to catch the killer before they strike again?&nbsp;</p> <p><i>Hexes and Vexes</i> is Book One of the Amethyst's Wand Shop Mysteries series. It is an urban fantasy mystery with an underlying slow burn romance.</p>"; 
